{% include '_header.twig' %}

<div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span9">

        <h1>About Pilex</h1>
        
        <h2>Pilex {{pilex_version}}<small>{% if pilex_name is defined %} - {{pilex_name}}{% endif %}</small></h2>
        
        <p>Pilex is a CMS that strives to be simple, fast, straightforward and enjoyable to use. Both for developers and content-editors. Pilex is Open Source, and as such it uses other Open Source components. If you are a developer you're very welcome to help in the further development of Pilex. </p>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/bobdenotter/pilex" class="btn btn-info" target="_blank"><i class="icon-github"></i> Pilex on Github</a>

        <h2>Used Libraries / Components</h2>
        
        <p>Below are the third party libraries that are used by Pilex. </p>

        <ul>
            <li><a href="http://silex.sensiolabs.org/">Silex - PHP micro-framework</a> and a lot of the 
                <a href="http://symfony.com/">Symfony components</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://www.doctrine-project.org">Doctrine DBAL</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://twig.sensiolabs.org/">Twig, flexible, fast, and secure template engine</a></li>
            <li>Various other PHP libraries, like: <a href="http://www.openwall.com/phpass/">Phpass</a>,
                <a href="http://brandonwamboldt.github.com/utilphp/">Util.php</a>,
                <a href="http://guzzlephp.org/">Guzzle, HTTP client for PHP</a>, 
                <a href="http://www.binarymoon.co.uk/projects/timthumb/">Timthumb</a>
            </li>
            <li><a href="http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap">Twitter Bootstrap</a> and 
                <a href="http://fortawesome.github.com/Font-Awesome/">Font Awesome</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://jquery.com/">jQuery</a> (and parts of <a href="http://jqueryui.com/">jQuery UI</a>)</li>
            <li>jQuery plugins, like: <a href="http://blueimp.github.com/jQuery-File-Upload/">jQuery File Upload</a>, 
                <a href="http://www.thewebsitetailor.com/jquery-slug-plugin/">jQuery Slug Generation</a>, 
                <a href="http://aehlke.github.com/tag-it/">Tag-it</a>, 
                <a href="http://www.shadowbox-js.com/">Shadowbox</a>
            </li>
            <li><a href="http://codemirror.net/">Codemirror</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://redactorjs.com/">Redactor</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

